channel.title: Version 5.12 :: Cap'n Hugo Relearrrn Theme
channel.description: 5.12.0 (2023-05-04) Change Change In th' effort t' comply wit' WCAG standards, th' implementat'n o' th' collaps'ble menu was changed (again). While Internet Explorer 11 has issues 'n display'n it, th' functionality still works. New New Support fer th' great VSCode Front Matter CMS extension which provides on-premise CMS capabilties t' Cap'n Hugo.
